Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBarclays%20warns%20these%20costs%20will%20significantly%20impact%20earnings%20estimates%20for%20top%20tech%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDepreciation%20costs%20could%20lead%20to%20AI%20stock%20price%20declines%20and%20valuation%20scrutiny%2C%20according%20to%20Baird's%20Ted%20Mortonson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20getting%20a%20boost%20from%20the%20booming%20AI%20trade%20are%20in%20a%20race%20against%20the%20clock%20to%20prove%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-return-investment-disappointing-goldman-sachs-report-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20massive%20investments%20in%20GPU%20chips%20are%20paying%20off%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20there's%20a%20little-talked-about%20issue%20that%20will%20make%20that%20endeavor%20even%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepreciation%20related%20to%20massive%20AI%20chip%20investments%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bnot-so-hidden%26quot%3B%20cost%20of%20AI%20that%20few%20investors%20are%20factoring%20into%20their%20valuation%20analysis%20of%20these%20companies%2C%20analysts%20at%20Barclays%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepreciation%20is%20an%20accounting%20method%20that%20allows%20companies%20to%20spread%20out%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20capital%20investment%20over%20its%20useful%20lifetime.%20That%20means%20that%20when%20a%20mega-cap%20tech%20company%20buys%20billions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20GPU%20chips%2C%20it%20doesn't%20immediately%20record%20that%20as%20an%20expense%2C%20but%20rather%20as%20a%20capital%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20lead%20to%20big%20profits%20upfront%2C%20as%20the%20capital%20outlays%20don't%20hit%20a%20company's%20profit%20and%20loss%20statement%20immediately%20but%20are%20rather%20recorded%20as%20a%20depreciation%20expense%20over%20the%20asset's%20useful%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lurking%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20useful%20lifetime%20of%20AI%20GPU%20chips%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20shorter%20than%20many%20expect%2C%20especially%20as%20AI%20chips%20go%20through%20an%20ever-accelerating%20innovation%20cycle%2C%20leading%20to%20higher-than-expected%20depreciation%20expenses%20that%20ultimately%20drag%20down%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20depreciation%20costs%20related%20to%20GPU%20chips%20will%20be%20so%20big%20that%20Barclays%20is%20trimming%20its%20earnings%20estimates%20of%20cloud%20hyperscalers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoogl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famzn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2FMETA-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20Platforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20as%20much%20as%2010%25%20heading%20into%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepreciation%20of%20AI%20compute%20assets%20is%20the%20biggest%20expense%20for%20these%20leading%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclays%20internet%20analyst%20Ross%20Sandler%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20this%20is%20a%20risk%20that%20may%20rear%20its%20ugly%20head%20as%20we%20start%20looking%20ahead%20into%202025%2C%20so%20we%20are%20flagging%20it%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20mega-cap%20tech%20companies%20spending%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20pricey%20GPU%20chips%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20massive%20depreciation%20costs%20will%20add%20up%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-price-outlook-earnings-demand-blackwell-chips-tech-stocks-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20shifts%20to%20a%20new%20product%20launch%20cadence%20of%20one%20per%20year.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20Nvidia%20has%20this%20very%20aggressive%20design%20cycle%20of%20roughly%20a%20year%20between%20major%20releases%2C%20all%20of%20those%20products%20have%20different%20skews%20and%20functionality%20and%20power%20profiles%2C%26quot%3B%20Baird%20managing%20director%20and%20tech%20strategist%20Ted%20Mortonson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20headwind%2C%26quot%3B%20Morton%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20big%20enough%20to%20impact%20valuations%20and%20send%20AI%20stocks%20lower%20over%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarclays%20estimates%20that%20Wall%20Street%20consensus%20is%20underestimating%20just%20how%20big%20the%20depreciation%20costs%20will%20be%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20bank%20expects%20Alphabet%20to%20record%20%2428%20billion%20in%20depreciation%20costs%20in%202026%2C%20which%20is%2024%25%20more%20than%20current%20consensus%20estimates%20of%20%2422.6%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Meta%20Platforms%2C%20the%20mismatch%20between%20Barclays'%20depreciation%20estimate%20and%20Wall%20Street's%20is%20even%20further%20askew%2C%20at%20%2430.8%20billion%20versus%20%2421.0%20billion%2C%20respectively%2C%20representing%20potential%20costs%20being%2047%25%20higher%20than%20expected%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGOOGL%2C%20META%2C%20and%20AMZN%20shares%20are%20between%205%25%20and%2025%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20consensus%20estimates%20perceive%20given%20this%20mis-modeling%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclays'%20Sandler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20don't%20think%20valuations%20are%20stretched%20vs.%20a%20historic%20bubble-y%20era%20like%202021%2C%20the%20AI%20boom%20has%20shined%20a%20brighter%20light%20on%20whether%20multiple%20expansion%20for%20big%20tech%20is%20warranted%2C%20so%20in%20light%20of%20this%20backdrop%20the%20depreciation%20(and%20hence%20valuation)%20disconnects%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20scrutinized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20accounting%20method%20mega-cap%20tech%20CFOs%20are%20using%20is%20extending%20the%20useful%20life%20of%20their%20server%20assets%20from%20five%20years%20to%20six%20years%20or%20more%2C%20as%20that%20would%20spread%20out%20the%20costs%20over%20a%20longer%20time%20period%20and%20dampen%20the%20hit%20to%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20that%20has%20its%20limits%20because%20of%20how%20quickly%20Nvidia%20is%20releasing%20new%20GPU%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20see%20any%20mega%20cap%20extending%20useful%20life%20of%20servers%20after%20this%206-year%20schedule%2C%20as%20GPUs%20cycle%20times%20are%20increasing%20rapidly.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20is%20mega%20caps%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20to%20absorb%20the%20higher%20cost%20of%20depreciation%20expense%20going%20forward%2C%20unlike%20the%20last%20few%20years%20when%20there%20useful%20life%20tweaks%20were%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandler%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20Mortonson%2C%20it%20all%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20return%20on%20invested%20AI%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWall%20Street%20has%20a%20big%20question.%20They%20are%20now%20spending%20over%20%24200%20billion%20and%20their%20CAPEX%20is%20over%2050%25%20up.%20Where%20is%20the%20return%20on%20invested%20capital%3F%26quot%3B%20Mortonson%20asked.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20so%20early%20in%20this%2C%20that%20combined%20with%20all%20the%20accounting%2C%20it%20all%20wraps%20up%20to%20return%20on%20invested%20capital%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20you%20see%20a%20return%20on%20invested%20capital%20till%20sometime%20in%202025%20or%202026.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortonson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out.%20I%20think%20the%20accountants%20got%20to%20take%20a%20hold%20of%20it%2C%20and%20there's%20got%20to%20be%20much%20more%20transparency%20between%20extending%20useful%20life%20of%20networking%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20servers%20ver