uld%20be%20working.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20thousands%20of%20Spaniards%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20Barcelona%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F07%2F08%2Ftravel%2Fbarcelona-tourism-protests-scli-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotest%20overtourism%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Protesters%20squirted%20water%20from%20toy%20guns%20at%20visitors%20sitting%20at%20sidewalk%20caf%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demonstration%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20years%20of%20surging%20visitor%20numbers%20and%20rising%20housing%20and%20other%20living%20costs%20in%20the%20seaside%20metropolis.%20Barcelona's%20mayor%20has%20declared%20skyrocketing%20rents%20and%20home%20prices%20the%20city's%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20experts%20say%20short-term%20rentals%2C%20including%20Airbnbs%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20restricting%20local%20housing%20supply%20and%20driving%20up%20prices.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0094119020300498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20published%20in%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Airbnb%20activity%20had%20increased%20rents%20in%20the%20most%20popular%20Barcelona%20neighborhoods%20by%207%25%20and%20pushed%20up%20home%20prices%20in%20those%20areas%20by%2017%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F09%2F22%2Ftravel%2Fbarcelona-airbnb.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartial%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20Barcelona%20in%202021%2C%20earlier%20this%20summer%2C%20the%20city%20announced%20it%20would%20aim%20to%20eliminate%20all%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcv22ygyzxnzo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapproximately%2010%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20registered%20short-term-rental%20listings%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20severe%20crackdowns%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20other%20tourist%20rentals%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Spanish%20city%20isn't%20alone.%20Cities%20around%20the%20world%20have%20implemented%20a%20range%20of%20regulations%20on%20short-term%20rentals%20to%20relieve%20pressure%20on%20the%20housing%20market%20and%20slow%20gentrification%2C%20among%20other%20objectives.%20Major%20cities%20like%20New%20York%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20and%20Vancouver%20require%20short-term-rental%20hosts%20to%20live%20in%20the%20homes%20they%20rent%20out.%20London%20and%20Paris%20limit%20the%20number%20of%20nights%20a%20host%20can%20rent%20out%20their%20home%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20look%20at%20three%20European%20hubs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Lisbon%2C%20Florence%2C%20and%20Amsterdam%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20have%20imposed%20relatively%20strict%20regulations%20on%20short-term%20rentals.%20In%20Lisbon%20and%20Amsterdam%2C%20early%20data%20says%20restrictions%20coincided%20with%20a%20drop%20in%20housing%20prices.%20In%20Florence%2C%20the%20impact%20isn't%20as%20clear%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20new%20phenomenon.%20Cities%20have%20been%20worried%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20short-term%20rentals%20on%20housing%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcities%2F2019%2Fjun%2F20%2Ften-cities-ask-eu-for-help-to-fight-airbnb-expansion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20pressure%20on%20lawmakers%20to%20do%20everything%20they%20can%20to%20tamp%20down%20the%20inflated%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20pushed%20many%20to%20pursue%20more%20aggressive%20policies%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rental%20platforms%20have%20opposed%20many%20of%20the%20regulations%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Airbnb%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Fairbnb-lawsuit-block-nyc-law-short-term-rentals-is-dismissed-2023-08-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunsuccessfully%20sued%3C%2Fa%3E%20New%20York%20City%20over%20its%20crackdown%20last%20year.%20But%20the%20company%20has%20since%20appeared%20more%20open%20to%20a%20new%20regulatory%20standard.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20called%20for%20an%20EU-wide%20approach%20to%20short-term%20rental%20rules%20that%20will%20help%20make%20regulations%20more%20consistent%20across%20the%20bloc%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Airbnb%20spokesman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221861546c-bc0d-4bbe-bce6-43082362c552%5C%22%3ELisbon's%20Airbnb%20ban%20may%20have%20kept%20housing%20costs%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20Portugal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportugal-bans-new-airbnbs-fears-becoming-some-sort-of-disneyland-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspended%20all%20new%20licenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20short-term%20rentals%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20alleviate%20pressure%20on%20the%20housing%20market%20from%20tourists%20and%20longer-term%20foreign%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20Lisbon%2C%20took%20action%20much%20earlier.%20The%20city%20ended%20new%20registrations%20for%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20some%20historic%20neighborhoods%20in%20November%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20ban%20may%20have%20slowed%20the%20growth%20in%20housing%20costs.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iza.org%2Fpublications%2Fdp%2F15706%2Fshort-term-rental-bans-and-housing-prices-quasi-experimental-evidence-from-lisbon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20November%202022%2C%20coauthor%20Jo%C3%A3o%20Pereira%20dos%20Santos%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20Finance%20at%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London%2C%20found%20that%20housing%20prices%20in%20Lisbon%20neighborhoods%20subject%20to%20the%20ban%20declined%20by%209%25%20compared%20to%20control%20neighborhoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Pereira%20dos%20Santos%20said%20restricting%20short-term%20rentals%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20control%20rapidly%20rising%20housing%20costs%20across%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%20The%20country's%20hugely%20popular%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-americans-buy-second-passports-amid-covid-politics-climate-change-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egolden%20visas%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20residency%20visas%20for%20foreign%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20have%20also%20boosted%20real-estate%20prices.%20Responding%20to%20its%20housing%20crisis%2C%20Portugal%20changed%20the%20terms%20of%20its%20golden%20visa%20program%20last%20year%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Feurope%2Fportugals-revamped-golden-visa-scheme-boost-investment-funds-2024-01-09%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexclude%20real-estate%20investment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20combination%20of%20restrictions%20on%20tourist%20rentals%20and%20foreign%20real-estate%20purchases%20could%20be%20contributing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-05%2Fportugal-s-runaway-home-market-shows-signs-of-hitting-a-ceiling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20slowing%20growth%20of%20housing%20costs%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20meeting%20its%20elevated%20demand%20for%20homes%2C%20Portugal%20needs%20to%20build%20and%20renovate%20lots%20of%20housing%2C%20Pereira%20dos%20Santos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20we%20do%20not%20see%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20short-%20to%20medium-run%2C%20an%20increase%20in%20supply%2C%20and%20if%20tourism%20keeps%20its%20momentum%2C%20I%20am%20quite%20worried%20that%20the%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%20will%20tend%20to%20deteriorate%20in%20the%20following%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20faster%20on%20licensing%20and%20rehabilitating%20housing%2C%20from%20both%20private%20and%20public%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf522fae-25c6-4578-b9dc-93f1e1b05af0%5C%22%3EAmsterdam%20home%20prices%20have%20leveled%20off%2C%20but%20it's%20unclear%20if%20that's%20due%20to%20caps%20on%20Airbnbs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmsterdam's%20less%20stringent%20policy%20has%20coincided%20with%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20of%20short-term%20rental%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20blanket%20ban%2C%20Amsterdam%20caps%20the%20number%20of%20nights%20hosts%20can%20rent%20out%20their%20homes%20at%2030%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20now%20around%205%2C000%20available%20listings%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20down%20from%20the%20city's%20peak%20of%2012%2C000%20listings%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20short-term%20rental%20analytics%20site%20AirDNA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20home%20prices%20have%20also%20slightly%20tapered%20in%20Amsterdam.%20Some%20experts%2C%20though%2C%20are%20hesitant%20to%20attribute%20that%20dip%20solely%20to%20enforcement%20of%20the%20Airbnb%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHousing%20prices%20in%20Amsterdam%20have%20leveled%20off%20and%20have%20cooled%20a%20fair%20amount%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20But%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20say%20whether%20this%20was%20because%20of%20the%20Airbnb%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gregory%20W.%20Fuller%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Groningen%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuller%20pointed%20to%20other%20housing%20measures%20in%20Amsterdam%20enacted%20over%20the%20same%20time%2C%20like%20a%202022%20ban%20on%20investors%20purchasing%20homes%20valued%20less%20than%20%24560%2C000%2C%20that%20eased%20pressure%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20affordability%20crisis%20still%20persists%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20just%20that%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20undersupply%20of%20affordable%20housing%20compared%20to%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Fuller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab9aec77-ee0b-4dc6-8eb8-301a970fa994%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlorence%20just%20reversed%20its%20ban%20on%20Airbnbs%20in%20the%20city%20center%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUneven%20enforcement%20and%20judicial%20challenges%20have%20muddied%20the%20impact%20of%20Florence's%20Airbnb%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-florence-italy-short-term-rentals-ban-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlorence%20banned%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20its%20historic%20city%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20two-square-mile%20neighborhood%20with%20iconic%20Renaissance%20buildings%20and%20museums%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20improve%20housing%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202016%20to%202023%2C%20short-term%20rentals%20had%20doubled%20across%20the%20city%20and%20rents%20had%20risen%2042%25%20over%20the%20same%20time%20period%2C%20Florence's%20then-mayor%20Dario%20Nardella%20told%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20July%20of%20this%20year%2C%20a%20regional%20court%20overturned%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20rushing%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20moment%20before%20the%20new%20mayor%20of%20Florence%20can%20impose%20new%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplications%20for%20Airbnb%20licenses%20in%20the%20city%20center%20jumped%2010%25%20just%20three%20days%20after%20the%20ban%20was%20overruled%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lanazione.it%2Ffirenze%2Fcronaca%2Fla-prima-giunta-di-funaro-pronta-la-delibera-airbnb-ma-dovra-rifare-tutto-liter-prossima-riunione-alla-verna-e3bf3e03%3Flive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItalian%20news%20outlet%20La%20Nazione%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20more%20coherent%20approach%20to%20this%20phenomenon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Antonello%20Romano%2C