in%20for%20a%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20walking%20into%20a%20store%2C%20browsing%20a%20catalog%2C%20or%20scanning%20the%20web%20for%20your%20favorite%20brands%2C%20imagine%20being%20able%20to%20shop%20just%20like%20you'd%20identify%20a%20song%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-shazam%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBecome%2520an%2520Insider%2520and%2520start%2Cshort%2520sample%2520of%2520their%2520audio.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusic%20discovery%20app%20Shazam%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20on%20demand%2C%20whenever%2C%20and%20wherever%20you're%20located.%20That's%20the%20vision%20behind%20the%20interactive%20shopping%20app%20Capsule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20e-commerce%20world%20has%20seen%20this%20concept%20before.%20In%202019%2C%20Amazon%20unveiled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-launches-shazam-for-clothes-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStyleSnap%2C%20an%20AI-driven%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20matched%20fashion%20photos%20users%20uploaded%20with%20products%20on%20its%20site.%20Brands%20like%20Asos%2C%20Wayfair%2C%20and%20Target%20have%20launched%20similar%20tools%20that%20rely%20on%20computer%20vision%20and%20deep%20learning%20algorithms%20to%20identify%20styles%2C%20shapes%2C%20and%20patterns%20from%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Capsule's%20goal%20is%20more%20ambitious%20and%20far-reaching%3A%20It%20aims%20to%20become%20the%20default%20destination%20for%20online%20shopping.%20Instead%20of%20relying%20on%20its%20inventory%20or%20partnerships%20with%20other%20brands%2C%20the%20company%20scrapes%20data%20from%20some%2020%2C000%20websites%20nightly%2C%20ingests%20it%2C%20and%20uses%20it%20to%20power%20its%20product%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapsule%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Michele%20Van%20Ruiten%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20its%20mapping%20out%20women's%20fashion%2C%20intending%20to%20own%20the%20space%20within%20two%20to%20a%20half%20y