roductions%20went%20live.%20Videos%20went%20viral%20in%20as%20little%20as%2048%20hours%2C%20as%20700%2C000%20subscribers%20to%20Pornhub's%20Girls%20Do%20Porn%20channel%20clicked%20on%205-minute%20teaser%20clips%20that%20drove%20traffic%20to%20Pratt's%20site%2C%20where%20100%2C000%20subscribers%20paid%20%2430%20a%20month%20for%20the%20full%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20say%20Pratt%20increased%20traffic%20by%20forwarding%20each%20victim's%20video%20link%20to%20her%20school%2C%20work%2C%20family%2C%20and%20social%20connections.%20Victims%20attempted%20suicide%20after%20finding%20themselves%20fired%20from%20jobs%2C%20hounded%20from%20school%2C%20and%20shunned%20by%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20my%20video%20had%20millions%20of%20views%2C%20and%20all%20my%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20acquaintances%2C%20and%20distant%20relatives%20knew%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20victim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Pratt%20also%20uploaded%20details%20from%20victims'%20original%20%26quot%3BBegin%20Modeling%26quot%3B%20applications%20%E2%80%94%20names%2C%20emails%2C%20family%20addresses%2C%20and%20even%20their%20height%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20favorite%20color%20%E2%80%94%20to%20websites%20he%20controlled%20that%20catered%20to%20so-called%20porn%20trolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trolls%20churned%20up%20still%20more%20traffic%20and%20attacked%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20mercy%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20victim%20described%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20would%20walk%20out%20of%20church%20and%20come%20back%20to%20her%20car%20to%20find%20notes%20in%20the%20window%20shield%20calling%20me%20a%20whore%2C%20slut%2C%20prostitute%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20victim%20testified%20at%20Wolfe's%20sentencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20now%2C%20long%20after%20the%202019%20demise%20of%20the%20Girls%20Do%20Porn%20website%20and%20its%20Pornhub%20channel%2C%20the%20videos%20remain.%20Victims%20say%20they%20still%20pop%20up%20when%20they%20Google%20their%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTen%20years%20later%2C%20I%20am%20still%20receiving%20harassing%20text%20messages%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said%20in%20March%20at%20Wolfe's%20sentencing.%20%26quot%3BI%20received%20one%20yesterday%20evening%20while%20nursing%20my%20newborn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb4cf0e5-5f06-4228-b203-e84fde0f1dfb%5C%22%3EUnmasking%20the%20traffickers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20its%20victims%20were%20humiliated%20publicly%20and%20by%20name%2C%20those%20running%20Girls%20Do%20Porn%20remained%20anonymous%20for%20most%20of%20the%20years%20the%20ring%20operated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tangle%20of%20fake%20phone%20numbers%2C%20addresses%2C%20and%20shell%20companies%20thwarted%20anyone%20seeking%20legal%20action.%20When%20the%20father%20of%20one%20victim%20emailed%20%26quot%3BJonathan%40beginmodeling.com%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20contact%20his%20daughter%20had%20%E2%80%94%20he%20didn't%20reach%20Jonathan%20at%20all.%20Instead%2C%20he%20received%20a%20lawyer's%20cease-and-desist%20letter%20with%20naked%20photos%20of%20his%20daughter%20attached%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20in%20California%20said%20in%20Pratt's%202019%20criminal%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20a%20former%20US%20Army%20cyber-intelligence%20analyst%20named%20Charles%20DeBarber%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202016%2C%20DeBarber%20was%20asked%20for%20help%20by%20a%20victim%20who%20wanted%20to%20know%3A%20Who%20had%20done%20this%20to%20me%3F%20Using%20publicly%20available%20data%20%E2%80%94including%202010%20domain-name%20registration%20records%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-the-panama-papers-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Panama%20Papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20DeBarber%20unmasked%20Pratt%2C%20Garcia%2C%20Wolfe%2C%20and%20the%20underlying%20corporate%20entities.%20All%20were%20sued%20in%20state%20court%20in%20San%20Diego%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20large%2C%20weird%20true%20crime%20story%20you%20kind%20of%20need%20a%20chart%20to%20explain%2C%26quot%3B%20DeBarber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20find%20Garcia%20through%20his%20Facebook%20page%2C%20by%20reverse-imaging%20a%20tattoo%20that%20appeared%20on%20his%20shoulder%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20videos%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Garcia%20was%20the%20actor%20who%20victims%20said%20told%20them%20to%20stop%20being%20%26quot%3Bwhiny%20bitches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba4b8f40-8882-445c-9497-4e6e9b509bb9%5C%22%3EA%20walk%20to%20Tijuana%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGirls%20Do%20Porn%20raked%20in%20some%20%2417%20million%20in%20subscriptions%20and%20content%20deals%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20would%20constantly%20punch%20holes%20in%20the%20walls%20and%20break%20computer%20monitors%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolfe%20said%20of%20Pratt%20in%20his%20March%20sentencing%20statement%2C%20describing%20his%20%26quot%3Bmanic%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bterrifying%26quot%3B%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPratt%20%26quot%3Bwas%20making%20millions%20of%20dollars%20and%20was%20driving%20around%20in%20a%20Lamborghini%2C%20living%20in%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20house%20in%20Rancho%2C%20Santa%20Fe%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolfe's%20defense%20lawyer%2C%20Jeremy%20Warren%2C%20said%20at%20the%20sentencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019%2C%20Pratt%20fled%20his%20life%20of%20luxury%2C%20crossing%20into%20Tijuana%20on%20foot.%20Weeks%20later%2C%20a%20federal%20grand%20jury%20in%20San%20Diego%20indicted%20him%2C%20Wolfe%2C%20and%20Garcia.%20He%20was%20still%20missing%20months%20later%2C%20when%20a%20state%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25022749-girlsdoporn-original-2016-verdict%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawarded%20%2413%20million%20to%20the%2022%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202016%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20pleading%20guilty%2