20to%20compete%20against%20global%20javelin%20stars%20in%20India.%20Despite%20not%20being%20at%20his%20physical%20best%2C%20he%20achieved%20his%20season's%20best%20throw.%20Chopra%20praised%20fellow%20athletes%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%20PR%20Sreejesh%20for%20their%20impressive%20performance%20and%20resilience%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fparis-olympics-2024%2Findiaparis%2Fits-a-dream-of-mine-to-neeraj-chopra-reveals-what-we-wants-to-do-after-paris-olympics-silver-medal%2Farticleshow%2F112442327.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRecycled%20Claims%20Earlier%20Proven%20Baseless%26quot%3B%3A%20Adani%20Group%20On%20Hindenburg%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20rejected%20the%20latest%20report%20by%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20as%20%26quot%3Brecycled%20claims%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20earlier%20%26quot%3Bproven%20baseless%20and%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B.%20The%20conglomerate%20said%20the%20allegations%20were%20aimed%20at%20personal%20profiteering%20that%20disregarded%20facts%20and%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20discredited%20short-seller%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20several%20violations%20of%20Indian%20securities%20laws%2C%20Hindenburg's%20allegations%20are%20no%20more%20than%20red%20herrings%20thrown%20by%20a%20desperate%20entity%20with%20total%20contempt%20for%20Indian%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20an%20exchange%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20show-cause%20notice%20sent%20by%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20last%20month%20to%20Hindenburg%20and%20its%20sole%20beneficial%20owner%20Nathan%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20Securities%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20had%20flagged%20violations%20by%20Hindenburg%20and%20Anderson%20under%20the%20SEBI%20Act%2C%20SEBI's%20Prevention%20of%20Fraudulent%20and%20Unfair%20Trade%20Practices%20regulations%2C%20and%20SEBI's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20Research%20Analyst%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFull%20Statement%20by%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindenburg%20Report%20-%20A%20Red%20Herring%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20latest%20allegations%20by%20Hindenburg%20are%20malicious%2C%20mischievous%20and%20manipulative%20selections%20of%20publicly%20available%20information%20to%20arrive%20at%20pre-determined%20conclusions%20for%20personal%20profiteering%20with%20wanton%20disregard%20for%20facts%20and%20the%20law.%20We%20completely%20reject%20these%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20which%20are%20a%20recycling%20of%20discredited%20claims%20that%20have%20been%20thoroughly%20investigated%2C%20proven%20to%20be%20baseless%20and%20already%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20reiterated%20that%20our%20overseas%20holding%20structure%20is%20fully%20transparent%2C%20with%20all%20relevant%20details%20disclosed%20regularly%20in%20numerous%20public%20documents.%20Furthermore%2C%20Anil%20Ahuja%20was%20a%20nominee%20director%20of%203i%20investment%20fund%20in%20Adani%20Power%20(2007-2008)%20and%2C%20later%2C%20a%20director%20of%20Adani%20Enterprises%20until%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20absolutely%20no%20commercial%20relationship%20with%20the%20individuals%20or%20matters%20mentioned%20in%20this%20calculated%20deliberate%20effort%20to%20malign%20our%20standing.%20We%20remain%20steadfastly%20committed%20to%20transparency%20and%20compliance%20with%20all%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20requirements.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20a%20discredited%20short-seller%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20several%20violations%20of%20Indian%20securities%20laws%2C%20Hindenburg's%20allegations%20are%20no%20more%20than%20red%20herrings%20thrown%20by%20a%20desperate%20entity%20with%20total%20contempt%20for%20Indian%20laws.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-%20Spokesperson%2C%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20came%20after%20SEBI%20chairman%20Madhabi%20Puri%20Buch%20and%20her%20husband%20Dhaval%20Buch%2C%20called%20the%20report%20an%20attempted%20%26quot%3Bcharacter%20assassination%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20the%20SEBI's%20July%20action%20against%20the%20short-seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESEBI%20chief's%20full%20statement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20Report%20dated%20August%2010%2C2024%20against%20us%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20state%20that%20we%20strongly%20deny%20the%20baseless%20allegations%20and%20insinuations%20made%20in%20the%20report.%20The%20same%20are%20devoid%20of%20any%20truth.%20Our%20life%20and%20finances%20are%20an%20open%20book.%20%C2%A0All%20disclosures%20as%20required%20have%20already%20been%20furnished%20to%20SEBI%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20disclosing%20any%20and%20all%20financial%20documents%2C%20including%20those%20that%20relate%20to%20the%20period%20when%20we%20were%20strictly%20private%20citizens%2C%20to%20any%20and%20every%20authority%20that%20may%20seek%20them.%20Further%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20complete%20transparency%2C%20we%20would%20be%20issuing%20a%20detailed%20statement%20in%20due%20course.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20Hindenburg%20Research%20against%20whom%20SEBI%20has%20taken%20an%20Enforcement%20action%20and%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20has%20chosen%20to%20attempt%20character%20assassination%20in%20response%20to%20the%20same.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadhabi%20Puri%20Buch%3Cbr%3E%5CnDhaval%20Buch%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2