%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NCP%20(SP)%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20claims%20phone%2C%20WhatsApp%20hacked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723365771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112441898%2Cimgsize-97004.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fplease-do-not-message-or-call-me-phone-whatsapp-hacked-claims-ncp-sp-mp-supriya-sule%2Farticleshow%2F112441861.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NCP%20(SP)%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20her%20phone%20and%20WhatsApp%20had%20been%20hacked.%20She%20requested%20people%20not%20to%20message%20or%20call%20her%20and%20announced%20she%20would%20file%20a%20police%20complaint.%20A%20source%20close%20to%20the%20leader%20confirmed%20that%20an%20online%20police%20complaint%20regarding%20the%20hacking%20had%20been%20lodged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Eye%20Injuries%2C%20Neck%20Bone%20Broken'%3A%20Chilling%20Details%20In%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%20raped%20and%20murdered%20on%20duty%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20had%20multiple%20injury%20marks%20suggesting%20violent%20assault%2C%20an%20initial%20autopsy%20report%20has%20revealed.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20was%20bleeding%20from%20both%20her%20eyes%20and%20mouth%2C%20injuries%20over%20the%20face%20and%20nail.%20The%20victim%20was%20also%20bleeding%20from%20her%20private%20parts.%20She%20also%20has%20injuries%20in%20her%20belly%2C%20left%20leg...%20neck%2C%20in%20her%20right%20hand%2C%20ring%20finger%20and...%20lips%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20It%20also%20ruled%20out%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20definitely%20not%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%3B%20the%20woman%20was%20murdered%20following%20sexual%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20neck%20bone%20was%20also%20found%20broken.%20It%20seems%20that%20she%20was%20first%20strangulated%20and%20then%20smothered%20to%20death.%20We%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20full%20report%20of%20the%20autopsy%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20police%20officer%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crime%20that%20has%20shaken%20the%20state%20and%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20by%20doctors.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20targeted%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20over%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital.%20The%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20responded%20that%20it%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20strict%20punishment%20for%20the%20perpetrator%20and%20said%20it%20is%20open%20to%20a%20central%20agency%20investigation%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20was%20a%20postgraduate%20trainee%20of%20chest%20medicine%20and%20was%20on%20night%20duty%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20on%20Friday%20morning%20at%20a%20seminar%20hall%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20at%20the%20hospital%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20dinner%20with%20her%20juniors%20around%202%20am.%20She%20then%20went%20to%20the%20seminar%20room%20since%20there%20is%20no%20separate%20on-call%20room%20to%20take%20some%20rest.%20In%20the%20morning%2C%20we%20found%20her%20body%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20reports%2C%20is%20a%20civic%20volunteer.%20The%20police%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20confirm%20this%20and%20said%20that%20he%20is%20only%20a%20criminal%20for%20them.%20The%20accused%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20was%20tracked%20down%20after%20police%20found%20a%20bluetooth%20headset%20at%20the%20crime%20scene.%20Police%20then%20tracked%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20that%20placed%20him%20at%20the%20crime%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20demanding%20a%20CBI%20probe.%20Union%20Minister%20and%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20hide%20the%20data%20in%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records.%20But%20the%20kind%20of%20incidents%20that%20are%20happening%20prove%20that%20they%20(women)%20are%20not%20in%20a%20good%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20said%20they%20are%20open%20to%20a%20probe%20by%20any%20agency.%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20assured%20that%20she%20will%20seek%20death%20penalty%20for%20the%20perpetrator.%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20and%20Trinamool%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20those%20convicted%20in%20such%20cases%20should%20be%20given%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20punishment%20or%20encounter%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20should%20bring%20in%20an%20ordinance%20calling%20for%20immediate%20action%20against%20such%20culprits.%20This%20could%20be%20made%20into%20an%20amendment%20after%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20will%20support%20such%20a%20law.%20He%20hoped%20that%20the%20other%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%2C%20would%20have%20no%20objection%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20said%20such%20a%20law%20would%20prevent%20prolonged%20trials%20that%20can%20last%20five%20to%20six%20years%20and%20save%20taxpayers'%20money.%20%26quot%3BThese%20rapists%2C%20who%20don't%20deserve%20to%20live%20in%20society%2C%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20either%20through%20encounter%20or%20by%20hanging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723365660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg5rmc8fo_kolkata-doctors_625x300_11_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news