eeraj's%20Golden%20Verdict%20On%20Mother's%20%26quot%3BLike%20My%20Son%26quot%3B%20Remark%20For%20Arshad%20Nadeem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStar%20javelin%20thrower%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20hoped%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20prominent%20international%20names%20in%20India%20sooner%20than%20later%20following%20his%20silver%20medal-winning%20effort%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Chopra%20bagged%20the%20silver%20at%20the%20Paris%20showpiece%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2089.45m%20behind%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%2C%20who%20hurled%20the%20javelin%20to%2092.97m%2C%20an%20Olympic%20record.%20Anderson%20Peters%20of%20Grenada%20came%20third%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2088.54m%20among%20the%20field%20that%20included%20some%20high-profile%20javelin%20throwers%20like%20Julian%20Webber%2C%20Jakub%20Vadlejch%20and%20Julius%20Yego.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20dream%20of%20mine%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20international%20stars%20in%20India.%20Hopefully%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20international%20competition%20soon%20in%20India%20and%20I%20can%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20during%20an%20interactive%20session%20with%20fans%20organised%20by%20the%20Olympics.com%20But%20before%20that%2C%20Chopra%2C%20whose%20silver%20was%20his%20second%20successive%20Olympics%20medal%20after%20the%20gold%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20certain%20areas%20of%20his%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20entering%20a%20new%20season%20now.%20So%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20that%20much%20time%20to%20change%20training%20methods%20or%20technique.%20But%20I%20hope%20to%20improve%20upon%20a%20couple%20of%20areas%2C%20especially%20the%20line%20of%20the%20javelin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20the%20correct%20angle%20of%20throwing%20so%20that%20I%20get%20more%20power%20in%20my%20throw.%20I%20will%20certainly%20work%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20all%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games%20final%20despite%20being%20below%20his%20best%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20body%20conditions%20(of%20his)%20were%20tough.%20But%20when%20Arshad%20made%20that%20throw...I%20was%20able%20to%20hit%20my%20season's%20best%20because%20the%20thought%20was%20set%20in%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20had%20to%20give%20the%20best%20throw%20because%20the%20competition%20had%20already%20become%20very%20tough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMothers%20of%20Chopra%20and%20Nadeem%20had%20taken%20the%20social%20media%20by%20storm%20as%20they%20showered%20affection%20on%20each%20other's%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20said%20his%20mother%20always%20spoke%20from%20her%20heart%20as%20she%20to%20date%20remained%20a%20simple%20rural%20soul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mother%E2%80%A6she%20always%20stayed%20in%20a%20village%20before%20and%20after%20her%20marriage.%20She%20is%20not%20familiar%20with%20social%20media%20and%20things%20like%20that.%20She%20often%20speaks%20from%20her%20heart.%20But%20she%20understands%20what%20families%20of%20athletes%2C%20even%20from%20different%20countries%2C%20feel%20towards%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPraise%20for%20Sreejesh%2C%20Manu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20lauded%20shooter%20Manu%20Bhaker%20for%20showing%20perseverance%20to%20grab%20two%20bronze%20medals%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games%20after%20experiencing%20utter%20disappointment%20in%20the%20Tokyo%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20Manu%20Bhaker%20prepared%20her%20mind%20and%20came%20from%20her%20Tokyo%20setback%20is%20impressive.%20Her%20mindset%20appeared%20to%20be%20very%20strong%20this%20time%20while%20taking%20part%20in%20back-to-back%20competitions.%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20a%20start%20for%20her%20because%20I%20saw%20even%20people%20over%2050%20(age)%20were%20participating%20in%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20Manu%20will%20play%20in%20a%20lot%20more%20competitions%2C%20bring%20a%20lot%20more%20medals%20for%20the%20country%20and%20change%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20medal%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20also%20hailed%20Indian%20hockey%20team's%20goalkeeper%20PR%20Sreejesh%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20top-level%20competition%20with%20a%20bronze%20at%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSreejesh%20is%20a%20very%20relaxed%20and%20funny%20person.%20He%20motivates%20younger%20players%20a%20lot.%20Sreejesh%20bhai%20had%20said%20that%20he%20would%20retire%20after%20the%20Olympics.%20The%20players%2C%20I%20think%2C%20also%20felt%20that%20they%20should%20win%20it%20for%20Sreejesh%20bhai%20after%20doing%20so%20many%20great%20things%20for%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20Sreejesh%20offers%20a%20fine%20example%20in%20tackling%20pressure%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20so%20many%20years%20of%20experience%20and%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20tackle%20the%20pressure%20situations.%20He%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20his%20zone%20when%20I%20met%20him%20before%20the%20bronze%20medal%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723365600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9pchlsi_arshad-nadeem-and-neeraj-chopra-pti_625x300_11_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Fits-a-dream-to-compete-with-other-international-stars-in-india-neeraj-chopra-6313011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mothers%20of%20Chopra%20and%20Nadeem%20had%20taken%20the%20social%20media%20by%20storm%20as%20they%20showered%20affection%20on%20each%20other's%20son.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Fits-a-dream-to-compete-with-other-international-stars-in-india-neeraj-chopra-6313011%22%2C%22