2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20signs%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20the%20top%20cop%20confirmed%20yesterday%2C%20citing%20the%20post-mortem%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoy%20had%20left%20behind%20his%20Bluetooth%20headphone%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20arrest.%20This%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20the%20main%20evidence%20against%20him%20even%20as%20CCTV%20footage%20also%20located%20him%20there%20at%20the%20likely%20time%20of%20occurrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20physical%20evidence%20has%20also%20been%20collected%20from%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-medical-college-kolkata-doctor-rape-eye-injuries-neck-bone-broken-chilling-details-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6312915%5C%22%3E'Eye%20Injuries%2C%20Neck%20Bone%20Broken'%3A%20Chilling%20Details%20In%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20extremely%20sad%20and%20angered%20because%20of%20the%20incident.%20We%20are%20with%20the%20family%20members%20and%20doctors.%20We%20are%20following%20a%20transparent%20investigation%20process.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20demand%20from%20the%20family%20for%20a%20probe%20by%20some%20other%20agency%2C%20we%20have%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20top%20cop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%2C%20conducted%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20magistrate%2C%20was%20videographed%20and%20her%20family%20members%20were%20present%20as%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20formed%20a%20seven-member%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20along%20with%20the%20forensics%20team.%20It%20is%20being%20headed%20by%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Detective%20Department%20and%20supervised%20by%20a%20senior%20cop%20in%20the%20rank%20of%20Additional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20Concerned%20Over%20Safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20their%20safety%20and%20security%20on%20the%20campus%20after%20the%20shocking%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20activists%20had%20held%20demonstrations%20at%20the%20hospital%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20students%20have%20maintained%20they%20won't%20allow%20politics%20inside%20the%20hospital%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20slugfest%20with%20both%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20ruling%20out%20police%20probe%20as%20inadequate.%20%26quot%3BThe%20arrest%20could%20be%20an%20eyewash.%20Only%20a%20CBI%20probe%20can%20uncover%20the%20truth%20and%20deliver%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Trinamool%20has%20urged%20against%20politicisation%20of%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20cheap%20politics%2C%20the%20BJP%20should%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20for%20speedy%20trial%20in%20case%20of%20heinous%20crimes%20like%20rape%20and%20as%20opposition%20we%20will%20support%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trinamool%20Congress%20National%20General%20Secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20as%20he%20sought%20a%20mechanism%20that%20ensures%20a%20seven-day%20trial%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20is%20circumstantial%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20should%20either%20be%20given%20capital%20punishment%20(hanged%20till%20death)%20or%20encountered.%20These%20people%20don't%20deserve%20a%20place%20in%20society%20and%20no%20point%20wasting%20money%20on%20them%20during%20a%20trial%20that%20continues%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20To%20Hide%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20called%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%20and%20despicable%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20anger%20of%20her%20colleagues%20is%20justified.%20She%20has%20urged%20the%20protesting%20doctors%2