%20change%20in%20the%20country%20and%20would%20have%20said%20this%20in%20her%20speech%20if%20she%20got%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20resigned%20so%20that%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20see%20the%20procession%20of%20dead%20bodies.%20They%20wanted%20to%20come%20to%20power%20over%20the%20dead%20bodies%20of%20students%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20allow%20it.%20I%20resigned%20from%20premiership.%20I%20could%20have%20remained%20in%20power%20if%20I%20had%20surrendered%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20Saint%20Martin%20Island%20and%20allowed%20America%20to%20hold%20sway%20over%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20I%20beseech%20to%20the%20people%20of%20my%20land%2C%20please%20do%20not%20be%20manipulated%20by%20radicals%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20undelivered%20speech%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saint%20Martin%20island%20has%20an%20area%20of%20just%203%20square%20kilometres%20and%20is%20located%20in%20the%20northeastern%20part%20of%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20It%20is%20the%20southernmost%20part%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%2C%20if%20I%20had%20stayed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20more%20lives%20would%20have%20been%20lost.%20I%20have%20removed%20myself.%20You%20were%20my%20strength%2C%20you%20did%20not%20want%20me%2C%20so%20I%20have%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20message%20to%20her%20party%20members%2C%20she%20has%20said%20Awami%20League%20has%20always%20bounced%20back.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20lose%20hope.%20I%20will%20return%20soon.%20I%20have%20lost%20but%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20have%20won%2C%20the%20people%20for%20whom%20my%20father%2C%20my%20family%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20speech%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Awami%20League%20leader%20had%20to%20resign%20and%20flee%20the%20country%20amid%20violent%20protests%20by%20students%20that%20started%20as%20an%20agitation%20against%20reservation%20and%20snowballed%20into%20a%20stand-off%20with%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government.%20Over%20400%20protesters%20were%20killed%20as%20the%20veteran%20leader%20tried%20to%20crush%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHasina%20Clarifies%20Razakar%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20remained%20in%20the%20country%2C%20more%20lives%20would%20have%20been%20lost%20more%20resources%20would%20have%20been%20destroyed.%20I%20made%20the%20extremely%20difficult%20decision%20to%20exit.%20I%20became%20your%20leader%20because%20you%20chose%20me%2C%20you%20were%20my%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20undelivered%20speech%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20she%20is%20pained%20by%20the%20targeting%20of%20Awami%20League%20leaders%20and%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bwill%20return%20soon%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAwami%20League%20has%20stood%20up%20again%20and%20again.%20I%20shall%20forever%20pray%20for%20the%20future%20of%20Bangladesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20clarified%20that%20she%20never%20called%20the%20protesting%20students%20Razakars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20statements%20during%20the%20protests%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20not%20the%20grandchildren%20of%20the%20freedom%20fighters%2C%20then%20who%20will%20get%20quota%20benefits%3F%20The%20grandchildren%20of%20the%20'Razakars'%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20word%2C%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20a%20paramilitary%20force%20recruited%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20during%20the%201971%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%2C%20sparked%20a%20massive%20backlash%20and%20the%20protests%20intensified.%20In%20her%20undelivered%20address%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20Awami%20League%20leader%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20called%20you%20Razakars.%20Rather%20my%20words%20were%20distorted%20to%20incite%20you.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20watch%20the%20full%20video.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHasina's%20Rocky%20Ties%20With%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Bangladesh%20had%20nosedived%20during%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20term%20so%20much%20so%20that%20Washington%20DC%20had%20said%20the%20January%20elections%20in%20which%20Awami%20League%20returned%20to%20power%20were%20not%20free%20or%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20before%20her%20exit%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20had%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bconspiracies%26quot%3B%20were%20being%20hatched%20to%20topple%20her%20government%20and%20alleged%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20man's%26quot%3B%20plot%20to%20carve%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BChristian%20country%26quot%3B%20out%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20allowed%20a%20certain%20country%20to%20build%20an%20airbase%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20then%20I%20would%20have%20had%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20resignation%20and%20escape%2C%20the%20US%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20has%20long%20called%20for%20respecting%20democratic%20rights%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20we%20urge%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20formation%20be%20democratic%20and%20inclusive.%26quot%3B%20Washington%20DC%20also%20said%20that%20the%20US%20greatly%20values%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20had%20condemned%20the%20violence%20against%20protesters.%20%26quot%3BWe%20condemn%20any%20violence%20against%20peaceful%20protesters.%20We've%20been%20watching%20this%20matter%20very%20closely%2C%20both%20from%20our%20embassy%20and%20officials%20here%20in%20Washington.%20(We)%20have%20been%20monitoring%20the%20protests%2C%20have%20seen%20the%20reports%20of%20people%20dying%2C%20being%20killed%20in%20the%20protests.%20And%20we%20again%2C%20call%20on%20the%20government%20to%20uphold%20individual's%20rights%20to%20protest%20peacefully%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Happening%20In%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20gone%2C%20an%20interim%20government%20under%20Nobel%20peace%20prize%20winner%20and%20Grameen%20Bank%20founder%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20has%20taken%20charge.%20Amid%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20he%20has%20asked%20students%20leading%20the%20protests%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20their%20efforts%20are%20sabotaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20standing%20by%20to%20make%20your%20efforts%20futile.%20Don't%20fail%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20protect%20Hindu%2C%20Christian%2C%20and%20Buddhist%20families%20from%20harm.%20%26quot%3BAre%20they%20not%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%3F%20You%20have%20been%20able%20to%20save%20the%20country%3B%20can't%20you%20save%20some%20families%3F...You%20must%20say%20-%20no%20one%20can%20harm%20them.%20They%20are%20my%20brothers%3B%20we%20fought%20together%2C%20and%20we%20will%20stay%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20development%2C%20Bangladesh's%20Chief%20Justice%20Obaidul%20Hassan%20and%20five%20other%20top%20judges%20on%20Saturday%20were%20forced%20to%20resign%20amid%20massive%20student%20protests%20demanding%20a%20revamp%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20top%20officials%2C%20including%20Dhaka%20University%20Vice-Chancellor%20Professor%20Dr%20Maksud%20Kamal%2C%20have%20also%20quit%20after%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723362000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Futc6dteg_hasina_625x300_07_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-awami-league-bangladesh-protests-could-have-stayed-in-power-if-sheikh-hasinas-undelivered-speech-6312541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20she%20resigned%20as%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20fled%20her%20Dhaka%20residence%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20wanted%20to%20address%20the%20nation%2C%20especially%20the%20protesters%20whose%20agitation%20forced%20her%20to%20quit%20the%20top%20j