es.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fphilippines-marcos-condemns-chinas-illegal-and-reckless-actions-over-disputed-reef%2Farticleshow%2F112440433.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fphilippines-marcos-condemns-chinas-illegal-and-reckless-actions-over-disputed-reef%2Famp_articleshow%2F112440433.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fphilippines-marcos-condemns-chinas-illegal-and-reckless-actions-over-disputed-reef%2Famp_articleshow%2F112440433.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEBI%20Chief%20Denies%20Hindenburg%20Report%3A%20%26quot%3BAttempt%20At%20Character%20Assassination%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20has%20strongly%20denied%20the%20latest%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations%20and%20insinuations%26quot%3B.%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20chairman%20Madhabi%20Puri%20Buch%20and%20her%20husband%20Dhaval%20Buch%20called%20it%20an%20attempted%20%26quot%3Bcharacter%20assassination%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20SEBI%20action%20against%20the%20short-seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20regulator%20had%20in%20July%20flagged%20violations%20by%20Hindenburg%20and%20its%C2%A0sole%20beneficial%20owner%20Nathan%20Anderson%20under%20the%20SEBI%20Act%2C%20SEBI's%20Prevention%20of%20Fraudulent%20and%20Unfair%20Trade%20Practices%20regulations%2C%20and%20SEBI's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20Research%20Analyst%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20chief%20also%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20disclose%20any%20financial%20document%20if%20sought%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20full%20statement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20Report%20dated%20August%2010%2C2024%20against%20us%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20state%20that%20we%20strongly%20deny%20the%20baseless%20allegations%20and%20insinuations%20made%20in%20the%20report.%20The%20same%20are%20devoid%20of%20any%20truth.%20Our%20life%20and%20finances%20are%20an%20open%20book.%20%C2%A0All%20disclosures%20as%20required%20have%20already%20been%20furnished%20to%20SEBI%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20disclosing%20any%20and%20all%20financial%20documents%2C%20including%20those%20that%20relate%20to%20the%20period%20when%20we%20were%20strictly%20private%20citizens%2C%20to%20any%20and%20every%20authority%20that%20may%20seek%20them.%20Further%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20complete%20transparency%2C%20we%20would%20be%20issuing%20a%20detailed%20statement%20in%20due%20course.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20Hindenburg%20Research%20against%20whom%20SEBI%20has%20taken%20an%20Enforcement%20action%20and%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20has%20chosen%20to%20attempt%20character%20assassination%20in%20response%20to%20the%20same.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadhabi%20Puri%20Buch%3Cbr%3E%5CnDhaval%20Buch%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723358520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fiqovmohg_madhabi-puri-buch_625x300_02_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsebi-chief-on-hindenburg-report-baseless-allegations-insinuations-6311778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20of%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20has%20strongly%20denied%20the%20latest%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations%20and%20insinuations%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsebi-chief-on-hindenburg-report-baseless-allegations-insinuations-6311778%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22