20draw%20a%20line.%20Sport%20is%20always%20governed%20by%20the%20rules.%20If%20you%20don't%20govern%20sport%20by%20rules%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhinav%20Bindra%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Folympics%2Fstory%2Fabhinav-bindra-hopeful-as-vinesh-phogat-wait-for-olympic-appeal-verdict-extends-2580444-2024-08-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20asked%20about%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20has%20appealed%20her%20case%20at%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20of%20Sport%20(CAS)%2C%20the%20result%20of%20which%20is%20still%20awaited.%20While%20Bindra%20too%20is%20keeping%20his%20fingers%20crossed%2C%20he%20has%20no%20clue%20in%20which%20direction%20the%20case%20is%20heading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20of%20course%2C%20I%20fully%20empathise%20with%20Vinesh.%20It's%20an%20incredibly%20difficult%20time%20for%20her.%20Everybody's%20heart%20is%20broken.%20We%20are%20all%20there%20for%20her.%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20her%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20know%20where%20this%20would%20end.%20I%20know%20the%20decision%2C%20now%2C%20has%20been%20postponed%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20one%20just%20has%20to%20be%20patient.%20I%20am%20not%20privy%20to%20the%20arguments%20that%20have%20been%20made%2C%20I%20am%20no%20legal%20expert.%20So%20patience%20is%20the%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20Bindra%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723355940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F57qlrl6_abhinav-bindra-and-vinesh-phogat_625x300_11_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fif-you-dont-govern-sport-by-rules-abhinav-bindras-blunt-take-on-vinesh-phogat-case-6312149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhinav%20Bindra%20sympathised%20with%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20but%20asserted%20the%20need%20for%20sports%20to%20be%20governed%20by%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fif-you-dont-govern-sport-by-rules-abhinav-bindras-blunt-take-on-vinesh-phogat-case-6312149%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20Man%20Sues%20YouTube%2C%20Meta%2C%20TikTok%2C%20Reddit%20For%20Being%20Too%20Addictive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20from%20Montreal%2C%20Canada%2C%20is%20filing%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%20against%20social%20media%20platforms%20TikTok%2C%20YouTube%2C%20Reddit%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20Facebook%20alleging%20that%20they%20are%20too%20addictive%20and%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20negative%20impact%20on%20mental%20health%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmontreal.ctvnews.ca%2Fmontreal-man-launches-class-action-lawsuit-against-social-media-platforms-for-being-too-addictive-1.6986404%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECTV%20News.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024-year-old%20said%20that%20he%20began%20using%20social%20media%20in%202015%20and%20experienced%20several%20problems%20with%20productivity%20and%20body%20image.%20According%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20he%20utilised%20social%20networking%20apps%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20every%20day%2C%20but%20he%20has%20subsequently%20cut%20that%20down%20to%20about%20two%20hours.%20%26quot%3BHe%20still%20finds%20that%20it%20has%20an%20effect%20on%20his%20productivity%20and%20his%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Philippe%20Brault%20from%20Lambert%20Avocats%2C%20the%20law%20firm%20representing%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202024%2C%20it's%20estimated%20that%20humanity%20as%20a%20whole%20will%20be%20using%20social%20media%20for%20a%20total%20of%20500%20million%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Brault%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20just%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20individuals%2C%20it's%20a%20widespread%20problem%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20firm%20took%20the%20case%20since%20this%20is%20an%20ever-growing%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Brault%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%2052%20per%20cent%20of%20Canadian%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%207%20and%2011%20use%20social%20media%2C%20and%20that%20platform%20owners%20must%20prioritise%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20their%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20aims%20to%20recover%20damages%20and%20punitive%20damages%20for%20the%20purportedly%20careless%20platform%20design%20of%20these%20companies.%20According%20to%20Lambert%20Avocats%2C%20the%20psychological%20weaknesses%20of%20users%20are%20exploited%20by%20the%20way%20social%20media%20programs%20are%20now%20designed%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20prolonged%20engagement%20that%20affects%20their%20daily%20lives.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20also%20looking%20to%20get%20this%20message%20out%20there%20by%20talking%20to%20the%20media.%20People%20have%20to%20understand%20the%20risks%20to%20the%20use%20of%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723354800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fe64db1co_social-media_625x300_11_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-man-sues-youtube-meta-tiktok-reddit-for-being-too-addictive-6312233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2024-year-old%20said%20that%20he%20began%20using%20social%20media%20in%202015%20and%20experienced%20several%20problems%20with%20productivity%20and%20body%20image.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-man-sues-youtube-meta-tiktok-reddit-for-being-too-addictive-6312233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris%20Leads%20Donald%20Trump%20By%204%20Points%20In%203%20Swing%20States%3A%20Poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20three%20months%20t