th%20independent%20voters%20viewing%20her%20as%20more%20intelligent%20and%20temperamentally%20fit%20to%20govern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20electoral%20college%20voting%20system%20considers%20Wisconsin%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Michigan%20crucial%20for%20Mr%20Harris%20to%20retain%20the%20White%20House.%20Despite%20Republican%20attacks%2C%20Democrats%20strongly%20support%20Harris%2C%20with%20voter%20satisfaction%20increasing%20by%2027%20points%20in%20the%20three%20Midwestern%20states%20since%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Democrats%20need%20to%20better%20communicate%20Harris's%20vision%20for%20the%20country.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-donald-trump-agrees-to-debate-kamala-harris-what-latest-polls-suggest-6298163%23%3A~%3Atext%3DYouGov%2520poll%26amp%3Btext%3DIn%2520swing%2520states%252C%2520Harris%2520and%2C64%2520per%2520cent%2520for%2520Harris.%5C%22%3Eprevious%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2060%25%20of%20registered%20voters%20think%20Trump%20has%20a%20clear%20vision%2C%20compared%20to%2053%25%20for%20Ms%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20still%20leads%20on%20handling%20the%20economy%20and%20immigration.%20However%2C%20Harris%20has%20a%2024-point%20advantage%20on%20abortion%2C%20which%20Democrats%20hope%20will%20mobilise%20voters%20in%20swing%20states%20like%20Arizona%20and%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20is%20viewed%20more%20favourably%20on%20democracy%20than%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20facing%20legal%20charges%20related%20to%20the%202020%20presidential%20elections%20and%20the%20January%206%20Capitol%20riots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723354560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fugf3uu1g_trump-harris-_625x300_22_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-leads-donald-trump-by-4-points-in-3-swing-states-poll-6311930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20ju