20or%20negligent%20act%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20last%20month%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20boy%20died%20of%20electrocution%20after%20coming%20in%20contact%20with%20a%20live%20wire%20in%20southwest%20Delhi's%20Bindapur%20area.%20He%20was%20returning%20home%20from%20a%20tuition%20class%20when%20the%20incident%20occurred%20on%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20man%20died%20of%20electrocution%20at%20his%20home%20in%20southeast%20Delhi's%20Mithapur%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20Rights%20Body%20Notice%20To%20Delhi%20Over%20Electrocution%20Cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20of%20India%20(NHRC)%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20Delhi%20police%20commissioner%2C%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20officials%20in%20connection%20with%20reported%20incidents%20of%20drowning%20and%20electrocution%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reported%20incidents%2C%20as%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20are%20indicative%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%20by%20the%20civic%20authorities%2C%20which%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20August%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NHRC%20said%20it%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20a%20media%20report%20that%20at%20least%2013%20lives%20were%20lost%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20including%20six%20due%20to%20electrocution%20and%20four%20due%20to%20drowning%20after%20falling%20into%20overflowing%20drains%20amid%20heavy%20rain%20%26quot%3Bmagnifying%20the%20creaky%20infrastructure%20and%20civic%20negligence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20also%20said%20it%20would%20like%20to%20know%20about%20the%20steps%20taken%20or%20proposed%20by%20the%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20that%20such%20painful%20incidents%20do%20not%20recur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompensation%20For%20Electrocution%20Cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%20regulator%20Delhi%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission%20has%20announced%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20in%20case%20of%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20Rs%20five%20lakh%20on%20more%20than%2060%20per%20cent%20disability%20due%20to%20electricity-related%20mishaps%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulations%20stipulate%20a%20range%20of%20compensation%20for%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20injuries%20to%20people%20as%20well%20as%20loss%20of%20milch%20and%20draught%20animals%2C%20birds%2C%20and%20poultry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20electricity-related%20accident%20causes%2040-60%20per%20cent%20injury%20to%20any%20person%2C%20he%20will%20get%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20as%20compensation%2C%20Rs%2025%2C000%20on%20hospitalisation%20for%20over%20a%20week%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20case%20of%20less%20than%20a%20week%20of%20hospitalisation%2C%20the%20regulations%20lay%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723354380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F8dqi24og_playing-ground_625x300_11_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fboy-playing-cricket-goes-to-get-a-ball-dies-of-electrocution-in-delhi-6311855%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2013-year-old%20boy%20died%20due%20to%20electrocution%20when%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20a%20live%20wire%20while%20playing%20cricket%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fboy-playing-cricket-goes-to-get-a-ball-dies-of-electrocution-in-delhi-6311855%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weekly%20Chinese%20Horoscope%3B%20Five%20Chinese%20zodiac%20signs%20that%20are%20lucky%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A172335