ous%20crime%20and%20said%20the%20situation%20in%20Bengal%20regarding%20safety%20of%20women%20is%20not%20good.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20hide%20the%20data%20in%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records.%20But%20the%20kind%20of%20incidents%20that%20are%20happening%20prove%20that%20they%20(women)%20are%20not%20in%20a%20good%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20and%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%20into%20the%20death%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20addressing%20the%20issue%20seriously%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20formed%20an%2011-member%20inquiry%20committee%2C%20which%20bizarrely%20includes%20some%20interns.%20It%20seems%20the%20government%20is%20either%20trying%20to%20cover%20up%20its%20negligence%20or%20is%20not%20taking%20this%20matter%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%2C%20too%2C%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20probe.%20CPM%20state%20secretary%20Mohd%20Salim%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20City%20of%20Joy%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20City%20of%20bhoy%20(fear).%20No%20one%20is%20safe%20under%20this%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%2C%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20condemning%20the%20gruesome%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool's%20ally%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20joined%20the%20protests.%20A%20video%20shared%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI%20shows%20Congress%20workers%20joining%20the%20doctors'%20protests%20and%20demanding%20that%20their%20representatives%20be%20included%20in%20the%20inquiry%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Has%20Trinamool%20Responded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20assured%20that%20she%20will%20seek%20death%20penalty%20for%20the%20perpetrator.%20Known%20to%20oppose%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20cases%20related%20to%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20has%20in%20this%20case%20said%20her%20government%20has%20no%20objections%20to%20investigation%20by%20a%20central%20agency.%20The%20state%20government%2C%20she%20has%20said%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20to%20hide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20and%20Trinamool%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20those%20convicted%20in%20such%20cases%20should%20be%20given%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20punishment%20or%20encounter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20should%20bring%20in%20an%20ordinance%20calling%20for%20immediate%20action%20against%20such%20culprits.%20This%20could%20be%20made%20into%20an%20amendment%20after%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20will%20support%20such%20a%20law.%20He%20hoped%20that%20the%20other%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%2C%20would%20have%20no%20objection%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20said%20such%20a%20law%20would%20prevent%20prolonged%20trials%20that%20can%20last%20five%20to%20six%20years%20and%20save%20taxpayers'%20money.%20%26quot%3BThese%20rapists%2C%20who%20don't%20deserve%20to%20live%20in%20society%2C%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20either%20through%20encounter%20or%20by%20hanging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Far%20Has%20Probe%20Progressed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20made%20one%20arrest%20in%20this%20connection%20and%20sent%20the%20accused%20to%20a%2014-day%20police%20custody.%20Reports%20say%20the%20accused%20is%20a%20civic%20volunteer.%20He%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20rape%20and%20murder.%20The%20case%20against%20the%20accused%20in%20based%20on%20circumstantial%20evidence%20and%20testimonies%20of%20doctors%20on%20night-duty%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20inciden