-caption%5C%22%3ETo%20date%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20rejuvenated%2040%20wells%20and%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFast%20forward%20to%202024%2C%20people%20are%20now%20using%20air%20conditioners%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20never%20had%20such%20harsh%20summers%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20up%20as%20his%20responsibility%2C%20Kapil%20started%20%E2%80%98SayTrees%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20creating%20urban%20and%20rural%20forests%2C%20and%20rejuvenating%20lakes%20with%20support%20from%20corporations%20and%20the%20community.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20planted%203.8%20million%20trees%20across%20the%20country%20and%20rejuvenated%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20founder%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20has%20achieved%20this%20feat%20through%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20revive%20Bengaluru%20to%20its%20initial%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20in%20detail%20about%20his%20motivation%20to%20start%20SayTrees%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20roads%20were%20covered%20with%20giant%20trees.%20The%20cover%20was%20so%20dense%20that%20one%20could%20not%20see%20the%20sun.%20One%20day%20when%20I%20was%20travelling%20from%20home%20to%20office%2C%20I%20was%20as%20usual%20looking%20at%20the%20tall%20trees%20on%20the%20roads.%20The%20other%20morning%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20all%20those%20trees%20were%20gone.%20It%20was%20disheartening%20for%20me%20as%20I%20valued%20them%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20trees%20were%20being%20chopped%20down%20for%20road%20widening%20and%20metro%20construction.%20Although%20the%20Government%20was%20transplanting%20them%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%20as%20a%20citizen.%20Otherwise%2C%20Bengaluru%20would%20become%20like%20any%20other%20Indian%20city.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20regret%20later%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20began%20visiting%20government%20offices%20to%20understand%20his%20role%20and%20capacity%20as%20a%20citizen.%20In%202007%2C%20he%20started%20planting%20saplings%20on%20weekends.%20Every%20year%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20began%20joining%20him%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20SayTrees%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20weekend%20initiative%20has%20now%20grown%20into%20an%20active%20group%20of%20100%20people%20who%20conduct%20afforestation%20drives%20across%20the%20country%20with%20community%20engagement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20that%20people%20come%20and%20join%20this%20movement%20to%20make%20this%20initiative%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20organisation%20began%20working%20on%20water%20conservation%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20sapling%20needs%20support%20for%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20including%20regular%20watering.%20However%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20after%20planting%20saplings%20during%20the%20monsoon%2C%20it%20became%20challenging%20to%20find%20water%20to%20sustain%20them%20in%20the%20summer.%20While%20working%20on%20our%20plantation%20projects%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20water%20conservation%20also%20needs%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERejuvenating%20the%20once%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20aptly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Lakes%E2%80%99%2C%20Bengaluru%20boasted%20a%20large%20number%20of%20lakes%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20kings%20and%20the%20British.%20Satellite%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Region%20Development%20Authority%20(BMRDA)%20in%202001%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%202%2C789%20lakes%20in%20the%20city.%20Over%20time%2C%20many%20of%20these%20lake%20areas