20year%20to%20clean%20it.%20We%20have%20created%20a%20grazing%20land%2C%20a%20green%20patch%20for%20birds%2C%20and%20a%20walking%20track%20for%20the%20community.%20Now%2C%20both%20people%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20enjoy%20peaceful%20evenings%20near%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20says%20it%20cost%20the%20organisation%20Rs%204%20crore%20to%20complete%20this%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20expensive%20affair%20that%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20through%20corporate%20support.%20We%20make%20sure%20to%20involve%20the%20community%20to%20ensure%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20rejuvenation%20efforts.%20The%20community%20acts%20as%20additional%20hands%20and%20eyes%20for%20us%2C%20because%20while%20rejuvenation%20is%20easier%2C%20maintaining%20the%20lake%20is%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20diverted%20some%20of%20the%20incoming%20sewage%20and%20kept%20the%20rest%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20water%20into%20the%20lake.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20sedimentation%20ponds%20and%20wetlands%20that%20filter%20the%20incoming%20water%20before%20it%20reaches%20the%20lake.%20Rains%20are%20only%20seasonal%2C%20so%20maintaining%20a%20consistent%20water%20flow%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20says%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKapil%20says%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20recharge%20groundwater%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20steps%20involved%20in%20the%20lake%20rejuvenation%20drives%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20first%2C%20they%20identify%20the%20lakes%20that%20need%20urgent%20rejuvenation.%20Secondly%2C%20they%20prepare%20a%20detailed%20project%20report%20(DPR)%2C%20which%20includes%20information%20on%20the%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20topography%2C%20ecology%2C%20funds%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20benefit%20the%20community%20and%20biodiversity.%20Thirdly%2C%20they%20obtain%20approval%20from%20the%20government%20authorities.%20Finally%2C%20they%20proceed%20with%20the%20restoration%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kapil%2C%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20lake%20can%20store%20up%20to%20200%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20every%20monsoon.%20Imagine%20gallons%20of%20rainwater%20flowing%20down%20the%20drain%20and%20flooding%20the%20city.%20Lakes%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20capture%20that%20rainwater%2C%20which%20can%20then%20support%20the%20city%20during%20the%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20miles%20away%20from%20India%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20in%20the%20US%20since%202015%2C%20but%20this%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20affected%20the%20organisation%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20only%20grown%20since%20then.%20Although%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20visit%20home%20often%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20my%20parents%20angry!%20%E2%80%94%20I%20ensure%20to%20return%20to%20India%20once%20every%20year%20to%20monitor%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20cannot%20do%20this%20work%20alone.%20Bengaluru%20alone%20has%20200%20lakes.%20If%20we%20rejuvenate%2010%20each%20year%2C%20it%20will%20take%20us%2020%20more%20years.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20have%20that%20much%20time.%20People%20can%20join%20hands%20with%20us%20so%20that%20together%20we%20can%20rejuvenate%20more%20and%20more%20lakes%20and%20be%20responsible%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVolunteer%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saytrees.org%2Fvolunteer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESayTrees%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20build%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20SayTrees)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22