nt%2C%20logo%20designing%2C%20to%20running%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20to%20selling%20burgers%20from%20home.%20His%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%20was%20fueled%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20solve%20problems%20rather%20than%20solely%20chasing%20financial%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20I%20wondered%20what%20I%20was%20really%20even%20chasing.%20Money%3F%20That%20would%20come%20even%20after%20I%20started%20focusing%20on%20solving%20real%20life%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20on%20top%20global%20environmental%20issues%2C%20Azhar%20found%20that%20there%20have%20been%20several%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20protests%20worldwide%20on%20plastic%20pollution.%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20have%20an%20alternative%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20curb%20plastic%20usage.%20While%20big%20brands%20can%20afford%20jute%20and%20cloth%20bags%20but%20medium%20and%20small%20businesses%20which%20comprise%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20Indian%20market%20continue%20to%20use%20plastic%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20plastic%20bags%20are%20its%20properties.%20It%20is%20water%20resistant%2C%20thermal%2C%20durable%2C%20light-weight%2C%20and%20has%20good%20tensile%20strength.%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%20that%20could%20mirror%20the%20properties%20of%20plastic%20while%20being%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cheaper%20than%20paper%2C%20cloth%2C%20and%20jute%20alternatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%98Bio%20Reform%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20startup%20that%20manufactures%20compostable%20bags%20using%20corn%20waste%2C%20sugars%2C%20cellulose%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20components%20into%20sustainable%20biopolymers.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20it%20has%20replaced%20over%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azhar%20is%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360465%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAzhar%20manufactures%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20on%20the%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20drew%20his%20inspiration%20from%20a%20biopolymer%20research%20paper%20dating%20back%20to%20the%201800s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20studying%20about%20a%20biodegradable%20polymer%2C%20PBAT%20(Polybutylene%20adipate-co-terephthalate)%2C%20that%20is%20derived%20from%20plant-based%20sources%20such%20as%20corn%20and%20potatoes.%20This%20for