re%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Azhar%20inaugurated%20his%20factory%20in%20Hyderabad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20Azhar%20inaugurated%20his%20factory%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReplaced%206%20million%20plastic%20bags%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20unit%20from%20scratch%20was%20itself%20challenging%20for%20Azhar.%20He%20had%20to%20manage%20the%20intricacies%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20business%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20balancing%20academic%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20inauguration%20day%2C%20my%20uncle%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20co-founder%2C%20quit%20the%20company%20citing%20some%20personal%20reasons.%20I%20tried%20to%20balance%20both%20my%20studies%20and%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20company%20%E2%80%93%20from%20collecting%20raw%20material%2C%20assisting%20workers%20to%20manufacture%20bags%2C%20delivering%20the%20products%20in%20the%20market.%20I%20used%20to%20sleep%20in%20a%20corner%20in%20the%20factory%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Azhar%2C%20who%20was%20then%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20his%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20a%20year%20but%20Azhar%20had%20to%20shut%20the%20factory%20down%20after%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20make%20profits%20to%20sustain%20the%20company.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20back%20to%20zero.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20had%2014-15%20backlogs%20in%20my%20engineering.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20balance%20both%20jobs%2C%20I%20failed%20at%20both.%20It%20was%20a%20stressful%20situation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20through%20sheer%20grit%20and%20relentless%20effort%2C%20the%20civil%20engineer%20not%20only%20cleared%20all%20exams%20but%20also%20secured%20a%20funding%20from%20an%20investor%2C%20and%20eventually%20revived%20his%20enterprise%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20company%20is%20manufacturing%204-5%20lakh%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345783%2Fyellowbag-in-madurai-traditional-tamil-cloth-bags-plastic-waste-krishnan-subramanian-gowri-gopinath-earn-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20Interestingly%2C%20Azhar%20says%2C%20these%20bags%20are%20compostable%20and%20can%20be%20decomposed%20within%20180%20days.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20his%20startup%20has%20replaced%20more%20than%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags%20by%20commercialising%20in%20the%20B2B%20chain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20clocked%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.8%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohd%20Sami%20Uddin%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Country%20Chicken%20Co%2C%20has%20been%20using%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20Sharing%20his%20feedback%2C%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20Prior%20to%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%2C%20we%20were%20using%20plastic%20bags.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20also%20tried%20other%20sustainable%20bags%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20they%20were%20neither%20food%20grade%20quality%20nor%20superior.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20the%20customers%20would%20complain%20to%20us%20if%20some%20sharp%20bones%20would%20pop%20out%20from%20low-grade%20bags.%20However%2C%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20meet%20all%20our%20requirements%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20sealed%20as%20well%2C%20similar%20to%20plastic.%20Besides%2C%20there%20was%20not%20much%20difference%20from%20the%20price%C2%A0%20point%20also.%20The%20plastic%20bags%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20whereas%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20cost%20Rs%20180%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20individual%20level%2C%20Azhar%20says%20that%20he%20has%20spearheaded%20a%20movement%20towards%20India%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289750%2Findia-bans-single-use-plastics-eco-friendly-alternatives-cups-cutlery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIssues%20related%20to%20plastic%20pollution%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20affecting%20aquatic%20life%20and%20animals%20anymore.%20Today%2C%20microplastic%20has%20reached%20our%20bloodstream.%20Bottled%20water%20contains%20microplastics.%20Addressing%20this%20is%20an%20important%20and%20urgent%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20I%20am%20able%20to%20contribute%20my%20part.%20It%20is%20sometimes%20taxing%20to%20not%20lead%20a%20regular%20college%20life%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20all%20worth%20it.%20I%20feel%20content%20when%20I%20go%20back%20to%20sleep.%20But%20much%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20make%20India%20plastic-free%2C%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mohammed%20Azhar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723208510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Azhar%20Mohiuddin's%20company%20'Bio%20Reform'%20uses%20innovative%20biotechnology%20processes%20to%20manufacture%20eco-friendly%2C%20biodegradable%2C%20and%20compostable%20bags%20that%20decompose%20within%20180%20days.%20Here's%20how%20they%20are%20replacing%20plastic%20bags.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360462%2Feco-friendly-biodegradable-bags-plastic-bag-replacement-bioreform-startup-hyderabad%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20an%20Indian%20Manufacturing%20Company%20Meets%2075%25%20of%20Its%20Energy%20Requirements%20Using%20Renewable%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Merino%20Industries.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustainability%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20end%20goal%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mindset.%20This%20philosophy%20is%20championed%20by%20Merino%20Industries%20Limited%20(MIL)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20manufacturers%20of%20decorative%20laminates%2C%20restroom%20cubicles%2C%20modular%20furniture%20and%20surfacing%20solutions.%20Their%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendly%20energy%20alternatives%20sets%20a%20precedent%20for%20other%20industries%20on%20how%20operations%20can%20be%20conducted%20without%20harming%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Prakash%20Lohia%2C%20CMD%2C%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20the%20transition%20from%20conventional%20energy%20sources%20like%20fossil%20fuels%20to%20green%20alternatives%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%20However%2C%20the%20key%20lies%20in%20implementing%20measurable%20changes%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20operation%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%20Sustainability%20Program%E2%80%99%20steps%20in.%20The%20initiative%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20and%20catalyses%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20becoming%20a%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20industry.%20The%20programme%20hinges%20on%20scaling%20business%20growth%20alongside%20societal%20prosperity%20and%20pro-environmental%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20laser%20focus%20on%20increased%20utilisation%20of%20green%20energy%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20air%20pollution%20reduction%2C%20circular%20economy%2C%20waste%20recycling%2C%20large-scale%20plantation%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20organic%20manure%20in%20agro-farming%2C%20the%20company%20is%20attempting%20to%20achieve%20the%20overarching%20goal%20of%20continuously%20reducing%20its%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20commitment%20to%20eco-consciousness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20strives%20that%20wealth%20is%20generated%20with%20minimalistic%20harm%20to%20the%20environment.%20To%20understand%20how%20it%20is%20achieving%20this%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20its%20%E2%80%98Triple%20Bottom%20Line%20Framework%E2%80%99%20that%20encompasses%20three%20key%20dimensions%20%E2%80%94%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Financial%20impacts.%20Success%20follows%20when%20each%20parameter%20is%20scaled%20in%20parallel%20to%20the%20other.%20Excellence%20lies%20at%20the%20convergence%20of%20economy%20and%20sustainability%2C%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0