%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1-1723194179-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360478%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20waste-to-energy%20plant%20at%20Hapur%20converts%20biomass%20into%20thermal%20energy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%20Program%E2%80%99%20ensures%20that%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20Bh%C5%ABmih%20(soil)%2C%20Apah%20(water)%2C%20Analah%20(fire)%2C%20Vayu%20(air)%2C%20and%20Aakasha%20(space)%20are%20impacted%20positively%20even%20as%20Merino%20makes%20strides%20as%20an%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20eco-friendly%20paradigm%20shift%20is%20not%20something%20recent.%20Merino%20Industries%20has%20long%20embraced%20eco-consciousness.%20Their%20five-decade-old%20commitment%20views%20planet-friendly%20practices%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinseparable%20part%20of%20economic%20activity%E2%80%9D.%20And%2C%20the%20success%20of%20these%20strategies%20is%20evident.%20Merino%20has%20managed%20to%20meet%2075%20percent%20of%20its%20energy%20needs%20through%20renewable%2F%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lohia%20highlights%20a%20three-pronged%20approach%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20this%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20trio%20of%20sustainable%20solutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20driving%20holistic%20growth%20in%20energy%20efficiency%20while%20transitioning%20to%20green%20fuels%20is%20to%20first%20identify%20the%20energy%20sources%20and%20then%20select%20alternatives%20from%20locally%20available%2C%20year-round%20options%2C%20Mr%20Lohia%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20any%20manufacturing%20or%20processing%20unit%2C%20energy%20is%20key.%20Most%20of%20our%20processing%20operations%20were%20traditionally%20dependent%20on%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20coal%2C%20or%20imported%20gases.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20Meri