ated%20from%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ed)%20Pioneering%20the%20use%20of%20biomass%20since%202005%20and%20turbine%20technology%20in%20Hapur%20which%20extracts%20energy%20in%20electrical%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries'%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20sustainability.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20roadmap%20has%20guided%20Merino%20Industries%20in%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20company%20has%20expanded%20its%20focus%20to%20water%2C%20air%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20primarily%20relying%20on%20renewable%20resources%20and%20energy%20sources.%20Merino%20I