0to%20Delhi%20to%20sell%20our%20apples.%20Later%2C%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eopened%20up%20in%20Himachal.%20Due%20to%20middlemen%2C%20no%20farmer%20ever%20gets%20the%20full%20value%20that%20he%20deserves.%20After%20my%20daughter%20started%20selling%20it%20online%2C%20things%20have%20completely%20changed.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20market%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Bansal%2C%20who%20has%20been%20farming%20since%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPained%20by%20what%20she%20saw%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20help%20her%20father%20get%20the%20right%20price.%20She%20asked%20her%20Instagram%20community%20(which%20was%20then%20about%2010%2C000)%20if%20they%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20buy%20their%20apples%2C%20freshly%20plucked%20from%20the%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aprajita%20Bansal%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAprajita%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20