ir%20problems%20in%20detail%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20spent%20over%20four%20months%20assessing%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20Bihar%2C%20Noida%2C%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sector%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20agriculture.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Knight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%20as%20of%202023%2C%20out%20of%20which%20over%2080%20percent%20are%20unskilled.%20When%20Chandrashekhar%20came%20across%20this%20statistic%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20major%20gap%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDigital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI